700666f-a.title: Bronx: Bronxwood Avenue - Varing Avenue
700666f-a.text:
Bronxwood Avenue (foreground ), north from Waring (riht) to
Mace Avenues. Also shown, in the backcround, is Public School
No. 89, at the S.E. corner of Colden and Nace Avenues. The view
is northeastward.
